00:26:29.000 --> 00:26:32.440
to help us quickly chart how
to deal with a circumstance.

00:26:32.440 --> 00:26:35.950
And why would we have that
function, do you think?

00:26:38.170 --> 00:26:39.470
&gt;&gt; Survival?

00:26:39.470 --> 00:26:40.770
&gt;&gt; It's evolutionary.

00:26:40.770 --> 00:26:42.070
&gt;&gt; Howard Ross: Yeah, for
survival, exactly right.

00:26:42.070 --> 00:26:44.820
Twenty thousand years ago, we see a
group of people by the waterhole --

00:26:44.820 --> 00:26:47.350
we had to determine instantly
whether it was them or us.

00:26:47.350 --> 00:26:49.020
