00:28:04.840 --> 00:28:06.140
So we create qualifications.

00:28:06.140 --> 00:28:08.180
So we say, for example,
college degree.

00:28:08.180 --> 00:28:09.520
So toss out Steve Jobs.

00:28:09.520 --> 00:28:10.820
Toss out Bill Gates.

00:28:10.820 --> 00:28:13.620
Toss out Mark Zuckerberg, you know.

00:28:13.620 --> 00:28:16.300
We have to be careful because when
