00:28:16.300 --> 00:28:18.720 position:56%
without realizing, we're also
limiting ourselves to see the people

00:28:18.720 --> 00:28:20.020
who follow the most
traditional path.

00:28:20.020 --> 00:28:23.690
And there are lots of different
