00:28:23.690 --> 00:28:25.960
But I want to talk for just a
moment about what we're discovering

00:28:25.960 --> 00:28:29.930
about why the brain
functions in this way.

00:28:29.930 --> 00:28:32.670
So if you imagine, we see something
in front of us, some person

00:28:32.670 --> 00:28:36.390 position:56%
or circumstance and immediately,
what happens is and we know this now

00:28:36.390 --> 00:28:37.690
because we can wire the brain

00:28:37.690 --> 00:28:39.900
on functional magnetic
resonating imagery and we can see

00:28:39.900 --> 00:28:41.560
