00:28:46.820 --> 00:28:48.120
This is the limbic system.

00:28:48.120 --> 00:28:51.480
If I use my hand as a brain model,
imagine this is the profile.

00:28:51.480 --> 00:28:53.020
The limbic system is
in where my thumb --

00:28:53.020 --> 00:28:54.740
